items.headline: Welcome to the Real Housewives Wikia
items.desc: The Real Housewives Wikia is a community founded by fans of the Real Housewives series of reality shows. The Real Housewives Wikia covers all the different series including Orange County, New York City, Atlanta, New Jersey, Beverly Hills, and Miami. For more information about all your favorite housewives, please join us.
